{"tid":756710,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本單身漢為談戀愛自建婚戀網  建站5年無人上鉤","createTime":"2018-07-26T08:40:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T10:40:42.000Z","uid":49391,"like":651,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"afdc8e8cc1d442df6469bfc7ecf7124697efc9dd","tid":756710,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"俗話說，人要倒霉&ldquo;喝涼水都塞牙縫&rdquo;。近日，日本綜藝節目採訪到一位33歲的單身男子，聊其婚姻狀況時，該男子表示，為了談女朋友，自己建設了婚戀網站，結果建站5年都還沒交到女朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180726_ljt_220_5/gamersky_05small_10_20187261532B0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180726_ljt_220_5%2Fgamersky_05small_10_20187261532B0.jpg&h=013751f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180726_ljt_220_5/gamersky_03small_06_2018726153509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180726_ljt_220_5%2Fgamersky_03small_06_2018726153509.jpg&h=42314095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自建婚戀網主頁<br />\n<br />\n　　該網站的篩選條件只能選擇男性、東京（該男子的居住地），雖然有30多條的搜尋結果，但都是他一個人的資料。網站還推出占卜功能，為用戶配對合適的對象。當然在這個網站裡不論你輸入什麼內容，結果依舊顯示他自己。即便如此，經過5年的時間，仍舊沒有姑娘與他進行聯絡，至今仍是單身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180726_ljt_220_5/gamersky_02small_04_2018726153E03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180726_ljt_220_5%2Fgamersky_02small_04_2018726153E03.jpg&h=3788f34d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n30人全部都是我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180726_ljt_220_5/gamersky_01small_02_201872615386D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180726_ljt_220_5%2Fgamersky_01small_02_201872615386D.jpg&h=d7e063fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搜索結果頁面（選項默認，無法改變）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180726_ljt_220_5/gamersky_06small_12_2018726153938.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180726_ljt_220_5%2Fgamersky_06small_12_2018726153938.jpg&h=a71b8abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戀人占卜功能<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/07/20180726_ljt_220_5/gamersky_04small_08_2018726153CCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F07%2F20180726_ljt_220_5%2Fgamersky_04small_08_2018726153CCA.jpg&h=716d15c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都已經5年了"},{"pid":"55ea64fd2f52b890bd910030bb91df43e81a00df","tid":756710,"uid":118623,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e430986fc6f8197d0f3b68cd93b52575bafc9b","tid":756710,"uid":169108,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b258fc131e85a101357f6baa36438a8e953ad35b","tid":756710,"uid":24853,"like":154,"dislike":3,"score":151,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:49:01.000Z","msg":"好撚毒"},{"pid":"856d5b308b29aaa401f258865473e251368ccf09","tid":756710,"uid":195169,"like":301,"dislike":1,"score":300,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T08:52:48.000Z","msg":"笑死左<br />\n節目出左街應該好多女搵"},{"pid":"22bb12cd932ec384c82a5818fe97f999a085782b","tid":756710,"uid":91156,"like":246,"dislike":14,"score":232,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bb895f52b9ce5cd2cc8ccd4f3201b6b73bc8f3c","tid":756710,"uid":49391,"like":309,"dislike":2,"score":307,"quote":{"pid":"22bb12cd932ec384c82a5818fe97f999a085782b","tid":756710,"uid":91156,"like":246,"dislike":14,"score":232,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:04:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T09:05:47.000Z","msg":"但人地唔係GAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p